document_data.name: Cat One-eye
document_data.mainbody: '''Cat One-eye''' was a thief in [[Damara]] and a member of the [[Assassins Guild of the Galenas]] in [[1359 DR]].
document_data.Activities: Cat, as a contract murderer, wandered Damara searching for the most difficult targets for assassinations. She could kill anyone who annoyed her.
document_data.Personality: Cat liked killing. She also found it exciting if the target was truly hard to hit.
